{
  "stem": "2170.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I was standing near my sister and near my brother-in-law-- and somehow I saw-- I don't know what happened in that moment-- but I think I grabbed the shoemaker because he had only two daughters.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the commander said, who is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he hold me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, this is my child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and then he went like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they walked out, the Romanian gendarmerie, all of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left us in-- inside in the building, which was my sister, my brother-in-law, and I, the shoemaker, his wife, and the two daughters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they took them all to-- back to Brailov, to-- 20 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on when I spoke-- the people of Zhmerinka in the ghetto, they saw everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did not touch them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They saw my whole family walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were crying, everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They saw my beautiful sister, Hannah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When they saw her walking-- she was a beauty, that the goyim used to-- they'll never forget how beautiful she was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And surrounded by police, gendarmerie, on the road in the middle of the way between Zhmerinka and Brailov, Gestapo already with the Ukrainian police came to approach them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they came-- also, somebody-- there was a man who had a girlfriend in-between the 300.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a Zhmerinka man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was running after them in a side that they would not see him as far as to Brailov.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He wanted to see what's going to happen to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was very brave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the middle of the road, not far from Brailov, he saw a Romanian soldier taking my sister away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he thought, maybe, he told her to get away and to run.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
